              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11505525475354386792"><strong>Blown away!</strong><br/><br/>This author definitely knows his suspense, drama, gore, horrors and brings them all together with human and beast. What an ending! Going to have to move onto the next...highly recommend this to all fans of modern horror! </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

<tr class="no_border feedFooterReview" id="update_comment_stuff_Review1397654519">
  <td colspan="2">
    <div class="updateActionLinks">
        <a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link1397654519" title="Flag this review as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=1397654519&amp;resource_type=Review&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F145152.The_Cellar">flag</a>





