        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2418150106" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15460069240639187829">A MAJOR let down. Juvenile writing. Poorly plotted. No major character development. Also, it was as if the book seemed to want to tell 3 different stories at once, couldn&apos;t decide which one to focus on, and therefore did a terrible job with ALL of them! --Jen from Quebec :0)</span>
  <span id="freeText15460069240639187829" style="display:none">A MAJOR let down. Juvenile writing. Poorly plotted. No major character development. Also, it was as if the book seemed to want to tell 3 different stories at once, couldn't decide which one to focus on, and therefore did a terrible job with ALL of them! --Jen from Quebec :0)</span>
